userdoc.notice: A factory contract for creating `IDisputeGame` contracts. All created dispute games         are stored in both a mapping and an append only array. The timestamp of the creation         time of the dispute game is packed tightly into the storage slot with the address of         the dispute game. This is to make offchain discoverability of playable dispute games         easier.
